lrzip-fe: Install suggestions

* either lrzip or lrzip-next must be in path.
  if both exist, lrzip-next will be used.
* lrzip-fe.sh can be run from any directory or put
  in /usr/bin or /usr/local/bin
* if colors are unreadable for any reason, use
  the enclosed dialog.rc file by copying it to
  $HOME/.dialog.rc

